                                   as.person("Alexandre Ywata de Carvalho"),
                                   as.person("Victor Maus")
                                   ),
         organization = "INPE - Brazilian National Institute for Space Research",
         address      = "Sao Jose dos Campos, Brazil",
         year         = "2021",
         url          = "https://github.com/e-sensing/sits",

         textVersion  =
             paste("Rolf Simoes, Gilberto Camara, Pedro Andrade,
             Lorena Santos, Karine Ferreira, Gilberto Queiroz, Felipe Souza,
             Alexandre Carvalho, Victor Maus,  (2021).",
                   "SITS: Data Analysis and Machine Learning using Satellite Image Time Series.",
